  "title": "Architectural Executive",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>· Supervision and coordination of projects/ project team through different project stages</p>\n<p>· Responsible for project costs and schedules</p>\n<p>· Involvement in design development</p>\n<p>· Incorporate codes, authority submissions, consultations</p>\n<p>· Contract administration and any other site operational and project management matters</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Desired Skills and Experience:</p>\n<p>· Bachelor’s degree in Architecture or relevant field (project management etc.)</p>\n<p>· Min. 3 years relevant working experience preferred.</p>\n<p>· Positive working attitude, self-motivated and passionate</p>\n<p>· Conversant with local building requirements and regulations</p>\n<p>· Good time management skills</p>\n<p>· Experience in high density housing and/or public housing</p>\n<p>· Due to need of local knowledge, only Singaporean/ Singapore PR preferred</p>",
